dialogue.library_intro: Mutsuki-class destroyer Mochizuki. I took part in several invasions as a member of the 30th Destroyer Squadron. I engaged in transport missions again and again while going through repeated repairs. Worked hard, didn't I?
dialogue.secretary2: The strategy isn't complete yet? Well, I don't mind.
dialogue.secretary3: Upper... Ah... T-there there... That sure was stiff~... Yeah, that was good.
dialogue.secretaryidle: Well, I'm ok, just tired from work. Was spacing out? Oh, don't worry, I'll be fine.
dialogue.secretarymarried: nn… I'm not really that kind of character… but, well, Commander, maybe you should take a quick break, or something.
dialogue.wedding: You really shouldn't be spending time and money on me… Now I just have to work harder…. But still, thank you.
dialogue.show_players_score: Something came in. A message, will you read it?
dialogue.equipment1: Oh~ this is nice... my body, feels, light?
dialogue.equipment2: Phew, nice... finally there's a little motivation.
dialogue.supply: Oh~ this is nice... my body, feels, light?
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Ah~ What a pain... I'm gonna sleep.
dialogue.docking_complete: Oh? Ah, the girl that were in repairs are healed.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new friend? Seems like a weird ship... I don't mind.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: Strategy completed. The fleet is back.
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Okay okay, the fleet is leaving~
dialogue.attack: Torpedo attack, huh... Ah... seems like a bit of a pain.
dialogue.night_battle: Fine...! It's about time I get serious!!
dialogue.night_attack: Line of fire is... it's ok... this will do...
dialogue.artillery_spotting: Line of fire is... it's ok... this will do...
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: Line of fire is... it's ok... this will do...
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: Line of fire is... it's ok... this will do...
dialogue.mvp: I was the best... just how tepid is this fleet... well, whatever. I don't feel bad.
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Seriously, I said it hurts a lot!
dialogue.sunk: Commander, the truth is... I.. had... fun...
dialogue.valentines_day_2015: Eh~, Valentine's? What a pain~. Well, I do have some chocolate, though. Wanna eat?
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Woah! Is it really a two years anniversary? So amazing, it's immpossibl... well, time to sleep.
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: So sleepy... The Rainy Season, huh? The sound of rain is really lulling. Let's go to sleep together, Commander.
dialogue.fall_2015: It's autumn~. Time for the autumn harvest. There's gonna be so much yummy stuff. So let's just do nothing but eat n' sleep.
dialogue.christmas_2015: The Commander too should drink, eat and sing together, yeah? It's a Christmas of joy today!
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: Everyone is busy in this December, it seems. Aah, ouch, Mikazuki, don't hit me.
dialogue.new_year_2016: Commander, Happy New Year! During New Years, you sure feel like taking it easy. No need for working. Right?
dialogue.setsubun_2016: Uwaaa, there are a lot of beans... Mikazuki sure seems to be busy. I'll help lighten her load, *chew* *chew*.
